acceptance_criteria: "typescript 7.x is the sole compiler in devDependencies; strict ESLint gate runs (typescript-eslint TS7-compatible or successor adopted); static-quality-gate.mts produces identical violation baselines under the new parser (docstrings, complexity, boundary ratchet all byte-identical or intentionally re-baselined with evidence); dependabot major-version ignore for typescript lifted; CI fully green on all legs"
